When you want to select a nested resource with special praameters.

   [ P.select
       [ P.resource "sites"
           [ P.resourceWithParams "streams"
               [ P.order [ P.asc "name" ]
               ]
               allAttributes
           ]
       ]
   ]
       |> toQueryString

   -- select=sites(streams(*))&sites.streams.order=name.asc
